Unit                                                     Charge / Unit
Upto 199                                             @1.20
200 and above but less than 400        @1.50
400 and above but less than 600        @1.80
600 and above                                    @2.00
If bill exceeds Rs.400 then a surcharge of 15% will be charged and the minimum bill should be of Rs.100/- 
Sample Test Cases
Test Case 1 
Input
50 
Output
100.00 
Test Case 2
Input 
300
Output 
517.50


